## 3. Local Environment & Port Assignments
To prevent local hosting conflicts when combining software on a single machine, each team member must configure their tools to use the following designated ports:

* **vLLM Server (Jalen):** http://localhost:8000
* **SillyTavern (Acho):** http://localhost:8001
* **n8n Middleware (Tanner):** http://localhost:5678
* **Unity Webhook Target (Megan):** http://localhost:5678/webhook/aot-chat

